com.example.habitapp.utils.recyclerview

Class UserAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<UserViewHolder>
      • com.example.habitapp.utils.recyclerview.UserAdapter

  • public class UserAdapter
extends androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<UserViewHolder>
    The UserAdapter is the adapter class for the UserRecyclerView, it holds the users that the recycler view displays as well as some other functionality.
